00:14:32.507 --> 00:14:35.688
I just want to be considerate of our upcoming speakers.

246
00:14:36.588 --> 00:14:36.868
So

247
00:14:37.728 --> 00:14:40.728
this work was really led by the first postdoc in my group, Hansol Kim.

