00:14:54.888 --> 00:14:58.048
health-related and lifestyle factors every two years, as well as diet every four

252
00:14:58.088 --> 00:15:01.928
years. And so Hansol's project, which was funded by the Massachusetts Life

253
00:15:02.008 --> 00:15:02.668
Sciences Center,

