00:15:03.708 --> 00:15:07.488
we did a nested case control study of 211 cases of MASLD and their

255
00:15:07.748 --> 00:15:11.528
502 controls, the majority of whom were unmatched

256
00:15:11.568 --> 00:15:12.088
